<TITLE> All ministries get climate focal points </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 6 (bdnews24.com)  The government has marked ministry focal points in to deal with climate change. Mentioning that establishment of the climate cell was progressing smoothly, finance minister AMA Muhith said in parliament on Sunday, "One focal point has been identified in each ministry." Muhith said the Climate Change Trust Fund and the Climate Change Trust Fund Policy have already been formulated. Moreover, implementation of different programmes was in progress in line with the policy, the finance minister said. The government has allocated Tk 7 billion for the climate change fund
